"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-boxing-2024-0531-1452330-moorehouse-edges-closer-to-olympic-berth-in-bangkok\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Aidan Walshwill have to win a four-man box-off if he is to become a two-time Olympian following his defeat in Bangkok in his last-eight encounter with Jordan's Zeyad Eashash.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 5, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aidan_O'Brien\", \"score\": 0.9998057033254819, \"rank\": 0.00019418380484084583, \"text\": \"Aidan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aidan_O'Brien\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aidan_O'Brien\"}, {\"begin\": 77, \"end\": 85, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9968305001435785, \"rank\": 0.00317957752682925, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 110, \"end\": 117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 3.959746066620854e-12, \"text\": \"Bangkok\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\"}, {\"begin\": 151, \"end\": 157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9998426889309112, \"rank\": 0.00015732182258961912, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Tokyo bronze medallist was fighting for a place in Paris but got undone by two refereeing decisions, which cost him a point in both the second and third round and ultimately a place in this summer's showpiece.\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 180, \"end\": 185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999952252, \"rank\": 4.832945959591279e-12, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 231, \"end\": 236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997153282, \"rank\": 2.8463212787127955e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Walsh comfortably won the first round but was deemed to be holding in the subsequent stanzas, which led to a 4:1 split-decision victory for his Jordanian opponent, who progresses to Paris.\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 573, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997153282, \"rank\": 2.8463212787127955e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Belfast man must now come through a box-off with the other three defeated last-eight contestants for the one remaining place in the 71kg division.\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 585, \"end\": 592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\", \"score\": 0.999999976667141, \"rank\": 2.2043872451070165e-08, \"text\": \"Belfast\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gr\\u00e1inne Walshis one bout away from booking her spot at the 2024 Olympics after a dominant victory over Seda Sanago in their last-16 bout.\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 836, \"end\": 840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seda_Sayan\", \"score\": 0.9998247141575495, \"rank\": 0.00016603510444879844, \"text\": \"Seda\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seda_Sayan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seda_Sayan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Tullamore welterweight outclassed her Ivory Coast opponent from start to finish, scoring a unanimous 5-0 win among the judges to edge a step closer to Paris.\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 1033, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 876, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tullamore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1655620172306661e-14, \"text\": \"Tullamore\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tullamore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tullamore\"}, {\"begin\": 1027, \"end\": 1032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997153282, \"rank\": 2.8463212787127955e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Victory in Sunday's quarter-final will seal her ticket to Paris.\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1093, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997153282, \"rank\": 2.8463212787127955e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier,Daina Moorehousemoved a step closer to the Paris Games with victory at the Olympic qualifying tournament in Bangkok.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1217, \"end\": 1224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 3.959746066620854e-12, \"text\": \"Bangkok\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Wicklow